    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced tofu</strong> to the <strong>marinade</strong> and give it a good mix, then transfer to a baking tray (or two!), keeping the remaining marinade in the bowl (you'll use this later!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
