    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>olives</strong> to the <strong>remaining marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>marinated vegetables</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>marinated vegetables</strong> to the baking tray[s] with the tofu and reserve the bowl</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until everything is cooked through and starting to char</p>",
