    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wipe the reserved bowl clean with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining garlic </strong>(not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!),<strong> remaining red wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> cold water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in the reserved bowl – this is your <strong>aioli</strong></p>",
