      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once your marinated vegetables are cooked through and charred, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the baking tray[s] and return to the oven for a final 1-2 min, or until wilted – this is your <strong>one tray Spanish-style tofu & pepper bake</strong></p>",
